&gt;&gt;Brian Fitzpatrick: Oh, that's good. The
other question was Mayor Emanuel gonna return,

01:15:50.670 --> 01:15:51.670
I believe?

01:15:51.670 --> 01:15:52.670
&gt;&gt;Dan Sinker: Yeah.

