&gt;&gt;Dan Sinker: Ah, you know, time vortexes
are funny things.

01:16:07.560 --> 01:16:10.160
&gt;&gt;Brian Fitzpatrick: OK. Well, Dan thanks
a lot for your time. I really appreciate it.

01:16:10.160 --> 01:16:12.310
&gt;&gt;Dan Sinker: Yeah. Definitely. Thank you.

01:16:12.310 --> 01:16:14.350
&gt;&gt;Brian Fitzpatrick: It was great talking
to you. Thanks.

